

=Bio=

"Keeping in mind the past, living for a future, regarding - action is now !

20 years from silkscreen designer, web, graphic, phography, mutimedia, videographer to Television Art Direction.

5 years ago quit all, and started to observe again the society, at the same time started to work on a documentary about creativity has a social empowerment tool that will be realeased in the middle of 2015.

Founder of a recent non-profit project - sede.pt . Sede will exist in a beautiful house in Porto, with the purpose to promote the iniciative of individual in a colective environment , through his actions of free and open knowledge, collaborative projects under FLOSS practices and p2p production, social activity, political and social activism by stimulation the creative processes, art and non-formal education, promote a culture of sustainable and integrated practicals, such as permaculture, the solidarity economy , open cooperativism, and critical thinking, questioning the city and the society. Interested in transnacional projects about privacy, open data, p2p production, ethic economy, empowerment, degrow and transition process."


